Package com.esprit.models.produits

Class Panier

java.lang.Object
com.esprit.models.produits.Panier
public class Panier extends Object
Is used to represent a shopping cart containing various products and users. It has several fields such as idpanier, quantity, produit, and users, which can be accessed through getters and setters methods. The class also provides a toString() method for creating a string representation of the panier object.
